{"type":null,"faqId":14623,"title":"通话声音很小或有杂音，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">请在信号较好的环境下通话。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手持模式下通话时，请适当调整握姿。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:2.0cm;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">将耳朵对准听筒的位置，可有效提高通话音量。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:2.0cm;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">请注意不要用手指或其他物体遮挡住麦克风（通常在手机底部）。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手持模式下通话时，请注意声源距离麦克风</span><span>10cm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">以内。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">耳机模式下通话时声音很小或有杂音，请使用华为标配耳机进行通话，非标配耳机可能会出现不兼容的情况。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">通话过程中按音量上键可以提高通话音量。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">请尽量在噪音干扰小的环境中进行通话。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若问题依然存在，请重启手机或备份重要数据后恢复出厂设置。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">若重启手机或恢复出厂设置后通话仍然有问题，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">华为会定期在官网发布最新软件版本，以优化软件性能，请您及时升级软件，以体验更好的手机性能。</span></p>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":137,"faqType":"通话与联系人","useful":1,"unUseful":11,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6665","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Calls-contacts","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1409217688000,"seriesProductName":"Holly-T00,Holly-U10","visitedTimes":1065,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"1","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}